  "title": "Air Travel - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_830326\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1993535_830326\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481855\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1993535_481855\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Air Travel</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6313129\">\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2647144\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2647144\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Several white, twin-engine propeller planes on the tarmac at Grand Canyon Airport\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/03689_2.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"\"/>\n<figcaption>Scenic tour airplanes on the tarmac at Grand Canyon Airport. NPS file photo. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1993536\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1993536\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 0);\">South Rim Airport</h2>\n<p><strong>Air Service</strong><br/>\nCommercial air carriers serve <a href=\"http://www.mccarran.com/\" id=\"http://www.mccarran.com/|\"><strong>Las Vegas</strong></a>, Nevada, <strong><a href=\"http://skyharbor.com/\" id=\"http://skyharbor.com/|\">Phoenix</a></strong> and <a href=\"http://www.flagstaff.az.gov/index.aspx?NID=1610\" id=\"http://www.flagstaff.az.gov/index.aspx?NID=1610|\"><strong>Flagstaff</strong></a>, Arizona. <br/>\n<br/>\nThere is limited air service into <a href=\"https://azdot.gov/about/grand-canyon-airport\" id=\"https://azdot.gov/about/grand-canyon-airport|\">Grand Canyon Airport</a> (10 miles / 16 km south of the park) from the Las Vegas, Nevada area.<br/>\n<br/>\nAll scenic air tours are based outside of Grand Canyon National Park. Both fixed-wing and helicopter tours of the Grand Canyon region are offered daily. <a href=\"https://azdot.gov/about/grand-canyon-airport/tour-operators-grand-canyon-airport\" id=\"https://azdot.gov/about/grand-canyon-airport/tour-operators-grand-canyon-airport|\">Learn more here</a><a href=\"http://www.azdot.gov/about/GrandCanyonAirport/tour-operators\" style=\"\">.</a><br/>\n<br/>\nFor those of you planning on flying your plane to the <strong>Grand Canyon Airport</strong>, the Arizona Department of Transporation has airport information at: <a href=\"https://azdot.gov/about/grand-canyon-airport/airport-approach\">https://azdot.gov/about/grand-canyon-airport/airport-approach</a></p>\n<hr color=\"#cccccc\" noshade=\"noshade\" size=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left\" title=\"\"/>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2647146\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2647146\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Grand Canyon Airport main terminal building\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/0145_2.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"\"/>\n<figcaption>Grand Canyon Airport's main terminal building, in the town of Tusayan, Arizona, south of the park boundary. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1993562\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1993562\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><font color=\"#336600\">North Rim - Nearest Air Service</font></h2>\n<p><strong>There is no longer an airstrip on the North Rim of the park.</strong><br/>\nThe North Rim of the park may only be reached by road.<br/>\n<br/>\nCommercial airlines serve <a href=\"http://skyharbor.com/\" id=\"http://skyharbor.com/|\">Phoenix</a>, <a href=\"http://www.slcairport.com/\" id=\"http://www.slcairport.com/|\">Salt Lake City</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.mccarran.com/\" id=\"http://www.mccarran.com/|\">Las Vegas</a>. There is also regularly scheduled air service into the <a href=\"http://www.flysgu.com/\" id=\"http://www.flysgu.com/|\">St. George, UT</a> Airport from Salt Lake City and Los Angeles. (St. George, UT is an 156 mile/ 251 km drive to the North Rim of the park.)</p>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: November 4, 2019</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
